# Keyboard Shortcuts

Move Focus Out of Virtual Machine

- Alt + Control

Move Focus Into Virtual Machine

- Control + G

Switch to Fullscreen

- Move focus into virtual machine.
- Alt + Control + Enter

Exit Fullscreen

- Move focus out of virtual machine.
- Alt + Control + Enter

# Unity

Exit Unity Mode

- Click on the VMware Workstation Task Bar icon.
- Click on the "Exit Unity" button.
